| Compile/Link  |                            | 6,070        | After all functions are compiled and linked into a single design                       |
|               |                            |              |                                                                                        |
| Unroll/Inline |                            |              | After user unroll and inline pragmas are applied                                       |
|               | (1) unroll                 | 4,152        | user unroll pragmas are applied                                                        |
|               | (2) simplification         | 3,660        | simplification of applied user unroll pragmas                                          |
|               | (3) inline                 | 3,385        | user inline pragmas are applied                                                        |
|               | (4) simplification         | 3,270        | simplification of applied user inline pragmas                                          |
|               |                            |              |                                                                                        |
| Array/Struct  |                            |              | After user array partition and struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied       |
|               | (1) array partition        | 4,368        | user array partition pragmas are applied                                               |
|               | (2) simplification         | 3,402        | simplification of applied user array partition & struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas |
|               | (3) aggregate/disaggregate | 3,402        | user struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied                                 |
|               | (4) array reshape          | 3,402        | apply array reshape pragmas                                                            |
|               | (5) access patterns        | 3,416        | array access pattern optmizations                                                      |
|               |                            |              |                                                                                        |
| Performance   |                            |              | After transformations are applied to meet performance pragma targets                   |
|               | (1) loop simplification    | 3,414        | loop and instruction simplification                                                    |
|               | (2) parallelization        | 3,404        | loops are unrolled or pipelined to meet performance targets                            |
|               | (3) array partition        | 6,567        | arrays are partitioned to meet performance targets                                     |
|               | (4) simplification         | 5,568        | simplification of design after performance transformations                             |
|               |                            |              |                                                                                        |
| HW Transforms |                            |              | After hardware transfomations                                                          |
|               | (1) lowering               | 5,573        | initial conversion to HW specific instructions                                         |
|               | (2) optimizations          | 5,669        | high level synthesis optimizations                                                     |
